technicalDetails.OS: Android 13: Comes with Android 13 for an intuitive, modern user experience with improved privacy controls., Customizable UI: Personalize your phone with dynamic themes, widgets, and enhanced notifications., Near-Stock Android: Offers a clean and bloatware-free interface for smooth and clutter-free usage., Optimized Performance: Lightweight OS ensures efficient performance and extended battery life., Privacy Dashboard: Provides detailed control over app permissions and data access for better security.
technicalDetails.Connectivity technologies: 4G VoLTE Support: Ensures high-quality voice calls and faster internet on 4G networks., Bluetooth 5.0: Provides faster pairing, improved range, and lower power consumption for connected devices., GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS: Accurate location tracking and navigation support., USB Type-C Port: Offers faster charging and data transfer compared to traditional Micro-USB ports., Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac: Dual-band Wi-Fi (2.4GHz and 5GHz) for stable and fast wireless connections.
technicalDetails.Special features: 1. HD+ IPS LCD Display Technology: The Motorola E32s utilizes an HD+ IPS LCD display which offers wider viewing angles and excellent color accuracy, providing a more vibrant and immersive viewing experience for all types of content., 2. Advanced Connectivity Options: Equipped with the latest connectivity features such as Bluetooth 5.0 and dual-band Wi-Fi (supporting 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz networks), the E32s ensures faster and more stable connections whether you're at home or on the go., 3. Dedicated MicroSD Slot: Unlike many modern smartphones, the Motorola E32s features a dedicated microSD slot that allows users to expand storage without sacrificing the dual SIM functionality, making it an ideal choice for users who need extra space for their files and media., 4. Water Repellent Design: The device comes with a water-repellent coating that protects against moderate exposure to water, such as accidental spills, splashes, or light rain, adding an extra layer of durability., 5. Biometric Security Features: For enhanced security, the Motorola E32s includes a side-mounted fingerprint sensor and face recognition technology. These biometric features offer users a quick and secure way to unlock their phones, access sensitive information, and authenticate transactions with just a touch or a glance.
technicalDetails.Resolution: The MOTOROLA e32s features a display resolution of 720 x 1600 pixels.
technicalDetails.Other camera features: The MOTOROLA e32s features a 16MP triple rear camera system, including a 16MP main lens for sharp, vibrant photos, a 2MP depth sensor for stunning portraits with natural bokeh, and a 2MP macro lens for capturing fine details up close. Enhanced by AI technology, this camera setup allows you to take high-quality images in various scenarios, from landscapes to close-ups, ensuring every shot is impressive and detailed.
